{
  "texts": [
    "This AI-based network would enable underdeveloped regions to effectively adopt advanced deep learning techniques for breast cancer diagnosis and prognosis.",
    "Sharing clinical and imaging data is crucial, yet there is a shortage of annotated, structured, and readily usable data currently limited to a few institutions.",
    "Establishing new imaging repositories, such as the Health Data Research Innovation Gateway, is essential to bridge this data gap.",
    "These repositories are critical to developing a robust data ecosystem that is necessary for creating innovative algorithms for early detection and treatment response prediction in breast cancer.",
    "AI in healthcare, especially in breast cancer diagnosis and treatment, faces several challenges."
  ]
}